headline: Dell (DELL) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of computer hardware and IT solutions company Dell (NYSE:DELL) jumped 4% in the afternoon session after several Wall Street analysts expressed confidence in the company by raising their price targets. Analysts at TD Cowen increased their price target on Dell to $125.00, while Bank of America lifted its target to $165.00 with a "buy" rating.
